660
00:57:00,560 --> 00:57:01,870
Omlouvám se.

661
00:57:02,800 --> 00:57:04,230
Jste v pořádku?

662
00:57:04,230 --> 00:57:06,820
Ano, děkuji.

663
00:57:06,820 --> 00:57:08,790
Kolik?

664
00:57:09,610 --> 00:57:10,590
Cože?

665
